iGorm : Cairngorm Automatic Weather Station iPhone App
======================================================

o Introduction
o Building
o More information

Introduction
------------

Building
--------
iGorm uses core-plot to display weather graphs so before you can build iGorm
you need to add the core-plot framework according to the instructions on
the core-plot wiki:
http://code.google.com/p/core-plot/wiki/UsingCorePlotInApplications

